# Project Plan – Testnet Marketplace

## Objective
Build a platform that helps users discover active testnets, track project rewards, and trade testnet tokens securely using Zama’s FHEVM.

## Core Features
- Testnet directory and discovery hub
- Token listing and exchange page
- Encrypted wallet balance tracking
- On-chain privacy protection using FHE

## Milestones
1. Draft architecture and smart contract structure
2. Prototype user dashboard
3. Connect testnet APIs
4. Explore privacy integrations via Zama FHEVM
5. Launch MVP and invite contributors

## Tech Focus
FHEVM + Solidity + simple data frontend (optional)
